## About AQUA THERM Nitra

AQUA THERM Nitra is the 24th International Trade Fair for Heating, Ventilation, Air Conditioning, Measuring, Regulation, Sanitary and Ecological Technology in Slovakia. This specialized exhibition serves the Slovak and Central European HVAC markets.

## Exhibition Focus

Heating Technology | Ventilation Systems | Air Conditioning | Sanitary Engineering | Environmental Technology | Building Automation

## Event Highlights

**400+ Exhibitors** and **10,000+ Visitors** make AQUA THERM Nitra Slovakia's premier HVAC and building technology event, offering comprehensive solutions for the construction and renovation sectors.

## Why Attend

Access the Slovak HVAC market, discover regional building technology innovations, connect with contractors and engineers, and explore business opportunities in Central European building services.
